come to terms with that.

03:27.320 --> 03:29.459
- [VEHICLE APPROACHES]
- It would just be fair to make sure...

03:29.483 --> 03:32.155
- Oh, look, it's Connie! Hey!
- Oh. Oh.

03:32.243 --> 03:33.643
- Hey!
- Whoop whoop!

03:33.668 --> 03:36.209
