we're all-in on this town.

04:04.478 --> 04:06.648
You could start with
opening your moving boxes.

04:06.673 --> 04:08.250
Oh, that? These are...

04:08.275 --> 04:10.109
Rio, remember when you went to the city

04:10.134 --> 04:11.242
for your mama's birthday?

04:11.267 --> 04:13.134
