04:13.159 --> 04:14.546
Well, you hurt Linda's feelings.

04:14.571 --> 04:16.375
You made her feel like you
didn't trust her to do it.

04:16.399 --> 04:18.586
I-It's just that there's
a guy in New York,

04:18.611 --> 04:20.812
and he... my colorist... um...

04:20.837 --> 04:23.505
and he does, like,
a very complicated layering process,

04:23.530 --> 04:24.782
in which he sort of, like, paints...

04:24.806 --> 04:28.664
If you really live here,
Linda has to do your hair.

04:30.124 --> 04:33.046
Okay, well, you know, Constance,
I-I can promise you one thing...

04:33.071 --> 04:35.234
We are gonna throw a kickass party.

04:35.259 --> 04:37.407
I don't think you get how
important this party is to us.

04:37.431 --> 04:39.086
When my husband passed,

04:39.111 --> 04:40.962
the last thing I wanted
to do was go to a party,

04:40.986 --> 04:42.531
but they brought the party to me.

04:42.556 --> 04:44.968
They knew what I needed before I did.

04:44.993 --> 04:46.531
That's what we do for each other.

04:46.556 --> 04:50.023
Now, if you want to be
a true Bucksnortiac,

04:50.048 --> 04:51.617
you have to listen to my advice.

04:51.642 --> 04:52.664
- Bucksnortiac.
- Okay?

04:52.689 --> 04:54.008
- I did not see that coming.
- No.

04:54.032 --> 04:56.554
These are the recipes.
These are the town's favorites.

04:56.579 --> 04:59.015
Oh, wow! That's a lot of butter. Huh.

04:59.040 --> 05:01.773
I wonder if I could substitute
some with... with applesauce.

05:01.798 --> 05:04.601
Get your head out your ass
and use the damn butter.

05:05.333 --> 05:07.799
[GRUNTING]

05:07.824 --> 05:10.851
[PANTING]

05:10.876 --> 05:13.234
Wow. You're going one mile an hour.

05:13.259 --> 05:14.259
Kay.

05:14.284 --> 05:15.916
Hope you're enjoying our truck,

05:15.941 --> 05:17.908
our house, the AC,

05:17.933 --> 05:19.799
- and our child.
- I am.

05:19.824 --> 05:22.725
Now, let's talk about how we're
gonna play the party, okay?

05:22.882 --> 05:24.973
Folks can't know that you're
living over at Mike and Rio's.

05:24.997 --> 05:26.683
- It's none of their beeswax.
- Agreed.

05:26.708 --> 05:28.051
But you know what'd
really sell everybody

05:28.075 --> 05:29.565
on us still being together?

05:29.590 --> 05:31.073
If I slept over at the house tonight.

05:31.098 --> 05:33.026
