05:36.333 --> 05:37.732
Do you hear me, mister?

05:37.830 --> 05:40.901
Don't cross over this boundary,
'cause I'm laying it down hard.

05:41.227 --> 05:42.706
Now, here's some meatloaf.

05:43.533 --> 05:45.714
