last pair of tight-whites.

05:47.770 --> 05:48.871
Coulda used these yesterday.

05:48.895 --> 05:50.402
- Oh, come on!
- Well, excuse my French,

05:50.426 --> 05:52.144
but I've been peen to
jean the last three days.

05:52.168 --> 05:53.229
[GEARSHIFT CLICKS]

05:53.254 --> 05:54.268
I have!

05:54.293 --> 05:56.433
I don't know, hon.
Maybe Connie was right.

05:56.458 --> 05:59.011
