anything important in them.

06:00.450 --> 06:02.028
We gotta show the town
that we're here to stay.

06:02.052 --> 06:03.808
- Oh. Yeah.
- We got to send a message like,

06:04.039 --> 06:06.284
"We're here, we're gonna die here,

06:06.309 --> 06:08.190
we're getting buried here on property."

06:08.215 --> 06:09.715
- Oh.
- In fact, I think we should consider

06:09.739 --> 06:11.253
digging some burial holes...

06:11.278 --> 06:12.526
- Plots?
- Plots.

06:12.551 --> 06:14.284
So when people drive by, they go,

06:14.309 --> 06:15.975
"They're in it for the long haul."

06:16.000 --> 06:17.414
- Maybe hold off on that?
- Yeah.

06:17.439 --> 06:18.697
You know what I mean?
Just, like, start with,

06:18.721 --> 06:19.986
like, unpacking the boxes first.

06:20.010 --> 06:21.322
- Y... Y... Okay. Start with unpacking.
- You know what I mean?

06:21.346 --> 06:23.048
And then consider plots.

06:23.073 --> 06:25.571
I assume you'll be attending
the kickoff party?

06:25.596 --> 06:27.181
Of course.

06:27.206 --> 06:29.337
Maybe we could go together.

06:29.684 --> 06:31.634
Maybe I will definitely say yes.

06:31.659 --> 06:33.868
To be clear, I'm currently saying yes.

06:33.893 --> 06:36.587
Hey, Connie, we unpacked
the last of our boxes,

06:36.612 --> 06:38.353
and I found my Rollerblades!

06:38.378 --> 06:39.455
- What, what?!
- Alright, girl!

06:39.479 --> 06:41.048
Whoa! There we go. I got you.

06:41.073 --> 06:42.173
- Sorry.
- Nice save.

06:42.198 --> 06:43.603
Yeah. So, um...

06:43.628 --> 06:44.782
We'll take all your butter.

06:44.807 --> 06:47.423
