bucket before kickoff.

07:09.979 --> 07:10.979
- Oh.
- For luck.

07:11.004 --> 07:13.618
Uh, I guess one question
I have is... is just...

07:13.643 --> 07:14.643
"Why?"

07:14.668 --> 07:17.702
Uh, in that, you know...

07:18.178 --> 07:19.204
why?

07:19.229 --> 07:22.470
