during the season opener party,

07:22.495 --> 07:24.532
and they caught that sucker
right before kickoff,

07:24.557 --> 07:26.345
and like magic,
the Huskers went on to win

07:26.370 --> 07:28.136
the national championship that year.

07:28.161 --> 07:30.261
Yeah, so, every year, we-we chase a pig.

07:30.286 --> 07:33.345
