sort of enjoy being, uh,

07:33.370 --> 07:35.728
chased around and smushed
into a bucket for luck, or...

07:35.753 --> 07:38.337
No, no, no. She hates it.
That's why she runs so fast.

07:38.362 --> 07:40.235
- Duh!
- Sure. And hypothetically speaking...

07:40.260 --> 07:42.657
- Hmm...
- If this year, we didn't chase the pig,

07:42.682 --> 07:44.327
- Mm-hmm.
- would that be a big deal, or...

07:44.351 --> 07:45.656
- Great question.
- Just imagine if

07:45.680 --> 07:48.655
