the Statue of Liberty lost her dress.

07:48.680 --> 07:50.069
- [LAUGHS]
- Imagine that. [LAUGHS]

07:50.094 --> 07:52.366
- Same... difference.
- [LAUGHS] Yeah. Okay.

07:52.391 --> 07:53.718
- Okay.
- Yes.

07:53.743 --> 07:56.163
About to whip up some of
Bucksnort's favorite treats.

07:56.188 --> 07:58.429
I'm gonna start with
Clara's "Dump Balls."

07:58.454 --> 07:59.960
- Oh.
- Jar of grape jelly,

07:59.985 --> 08:02.406
some barbecue sauce,
and frozen meatballs.

08:02.431 --> 08:05.227
- Great.
